 phong c\u00e1ch nh\u1eadt<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p>N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 v\u0103n h\u00f3a x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i, c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf <strong>s\u00e2n v\u01b0\u1eddn theo phong c\u00e1ch ki\u1ec3u Nh\u1eadt<\/strong> lu\u00f4n ch\u1ecbu \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng theo v\u0103n h\u00f3a c\u1ee7a nh\u1ecd. S\u00e2n v\u01b0\u1eddn nh\u1eadt lu\u00f4n tinh t\u1ebf, c\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u00e0 b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng. C\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u00e2n v\u01b0\u1eddn theo phong c\u00e1ch Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ecbu \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a th\u1eddi k\u00ec ph\u1ee5c h\u01b0ng, t\u00ednh c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1ee9ng v\u1eabn c\u00f2n n\u1eb7ng nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f9y bi\u1ebfn theo phong c\u00e1ch ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, t\u00ednh l\u00e3ng m\u1ea1n v\u00e0 bay b\u1ed5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o v\u00e0o trong thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_4342\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\">\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-4342\" src=\"http:\/\/trongcaycongtrinh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/trong-cay-xanh-cong-trinh.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 549px) 100vw, 549px\" srcset=\"http:\/\/trongcaycongtrinh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/trong-cay-xanh-cong-trinh-300x150.jpg 300w, http:\/\/trongcaycongtrinh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/trong-cay-xanh-cong-trinh.jpg 669w\" alt=\"trong-cay-xanh-cong-trinh\" width=\"549\" height=\"274\" \/><\/p>\n<p class=\"wp-caption-text\">s\u00e2n v\u01b0\u1eddn \u0111\u1eb9p gi\u00fap ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n, ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p>\u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean v\u00e0 kh\u00ed h\u1eadu th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, s\u00e2u r\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ebfn thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u00e2n v\u01b0\u1eddn. C\u00e1c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u00e2n v\u01b0\u1eddn theo sa m\u1ea1c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i c\u00e2y s\u1ed1ng l\u00e2u, c\u1ea7n \u00edt n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1n nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f4ng ch\u0103m s\u00f3c, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 sai l\u1ea7m khi b\u1ea1n ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c khu v\u01b0\u1eddn thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf theo phong c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee5n c\u00e1t v\u00e0 b\u1ee5i c\u1ecf. C\u00e1c khu v\u01b0\u1eddn sa m\u1ea1c c\u0169ng c\u00f3 v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p sinh \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u0111a d\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ec7 th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i v\u01b0\u1eddn kh\u00e1c. S\u00e2n v\u01b0\u1eddn nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt l\u00e1 to, m\u00e0u s\u1eabm t\u01b0\u01a1i t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi nhu c\u1ea7u n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i cao.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang tr\u1edf n\u00ean r\u1ea5t quen thu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ch\u00fang ta. Nh\u1eefng [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":594,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[5],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/cayxanh.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/443"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/cayxanh.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/cayxanh.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/cayxanh.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/cayxanh.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=443"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/cayxanh.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/443\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/cayxanh.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/594"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/cayxanh.websiteviet.vn\/